body:
Originally reported at https://github.com/psf/black/issues/4042#issuecomment-1852645541

Repro:
```
class Random:
    def func():
        random_service.status.active_states.inactive = (
            make_new_top_level_state_from_dict(
                {
                    "topLevelBase": {
                        "secondaryBase": {
                            "timestamp": 1234,
                            "latitude": 1,
                            "longitude": 2,
                            "actionTimestamp": Timestamp(
                                seconds=1530584000, nanos=0
                            ).ToJsonString(),
                        }
                    },
                }
            )
        )
```

Enabling just `wrap_long_dict_value_in_parens` turns this into:
```
class Random:
    def func():
        random_service.status.active_states.inactive = (
            make_new_top_level_state_from_dict(
                {
                    "topLevelBase": (
                        {
                            "secondaryBase": (
                                {
                                    "timestamp": 1234,
                                    "latitude": 1,
                                    "longitude": 2,
                                    "actionTimestamp": (
                                        Timestamp(
                                            seconds=1530584000, nanos=0
                                        ).ToJsonString()
                                    ),
                                }
                            )
                        }
                    ),
                }
            )
        )
```
